column1: #Text=Wikinews interviews Australian Paralympic skiers Jessica Gallagher and Eric Bickerton
#Text=Sunday , Wikinews sat down with Australian blind Paralympic skier Jessica Gallagher and her guide Eric Bickerton who are participating in a national team training camp in Vail , Colorado .
#Text=Wikinews reporters LauraHale and Hawkeye7 interview Australian Paralympic skier Jessica Gallagher and her guide Eric Bickerton
#Text=Jessica GallagherImage : Australian Paralympic Committee / Australian Sports Commission .
#Text=She 's competing at the IPC NorAm cup this coming week .
#Text=I 've got a race at Winner Park , but we are n't racing at Copper .
#Text=Your guide is Eric Bickerton , and he did win a medal in women 's downhill blind skiing .
#Text=Despite the fact that he is neither a woman nor blind .
#Text=No , he loves telling people that he was the first Australian female Paralympic woman to win a medal .
#Text=The IPC ' s website does n't list guides on their medal things .

#Text=Are they doing that because they do n't want — you realise this is not all about you per se — Is it because they are trying to keep off the able bodied people to make the Paralympics seem more pure for people with disabilities ?
#Text=Look , I do n't know but I completely disagree if they do n't have the guides up there .
#Text=Because it 's pretty plain and simple : I would n't be skiing if it was n't with him . Being legally blind you do have limitations and that 's just reality .
#Text=We 're certainly able to overcome most of them .
#Text=And when it comes to skiing on a mountain the reason I 'm able to overcome having 8 per cent vision is that I have a guide .
#Text=So I think it 's pretty poor if they do n't have the information up there because he does as much work as I do .
#Text=He 's an athlete as much as I am .
#Text=He 's as important as I am on a race course .
#Text=So I would strongly hope that they would put it up there .
#Text=We 've been having a great debate about whether or not you 've won a medal in women 's blind downhill skiing .
#Text=I found a picture of you on the ABC web site .
#Text=Both of you were there , holding your medals up .
#Text=The IPC 's web site does n't credit you .
